cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.IR, cs.MM

The paper deals with searching large image collections using hand-sketched queries, which falls under computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also uses a triplet convnet architecture and an RNN based variational autoencoder, which are common techniques in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also discusses real-time clustering and backpropagation, which are techniques commonly used in information retrieval (cs.IR) and multimedia (cs.MM).
